    "hohmann": {
      "title": "Hohmann transfer (about current body)",
      "description": "Classic two-burn transfer between near-circular orbits: Δv₁ = √(μ/r₁)(√(2r₂/(r₁+r₂))−1), coast half the transfer ellipse, then circularize. Assumes the start orbit is circular.",
