    "flyby": {
      "title": "Gravity assist (flyby)",
      "description": "Unpowered (optionally powered) swing through the current body's sphere of influence: coasts to the encounter periapsis and back out. The hyperbolic pass rotates the v∞ vector, changing the orbit about the parent body for free — the physics behind VVEJGA-style tours. Precede with a Transfer/Depart targeting a flyby periapsis; follow with the next Transfer. Reports v∞ in/out, turn angle δ = 2·asin(1/e), and the Δv gained.",
